the secret garden is a 1993 american-british drama fantasy film directed by agnieszka holland and starring kate &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; prowse , andrew knott , john lynch and maggie smith . it was written by caroline thompson and based on the novel of the same name by frances hodgson burnett . there are two previous film adaptations : a 1949 us drama film ; and the screen adaptation as a silent version filmed in 1919 , which starred lila lee and spottiswoode aitken .